OL,3,C'We're not giving up': The horse
OL,4,Criding centre saving endangered breeds
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports journalist Lauren
OL,7,FOstridge met Annie Rose, the owner of
OL,8,FCumbrian Heavy Horses.
OL,10,FA horse riding centre which
OL,11,Fspecialises in protecting Britain's
OL,12,Fendangered heritage breeds says it
OL,13,Fwill continue to fight on to battle
OL,14,Fsoaring costs - despite having to sell
OL,15,Ffour of its horses.
OL,17,FFor the past 20 years, Cumbrian Heavy
OL,18,FHorses has been a sanctuary for breeds
OL,19,Fsuch as the Scottish Clydesdale,
OL,20,FEnglish Shire, and the critically
OL,21,Fendangered Suffolk Punch.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
