OL,3,C'We're not giving up': The horse
OL,4,Criding centre saving endangered breeds
OL,6,FThe larger horses were once the
OL,7,Fengines of Britain's fields, but with
OL,8,Fadvancing technology their role was
OL,9,Freplaced with tractors and other
OL,10,Ffarming machinery, which has
OL,11,Fcontributed to dwindling numbers.
OL,13,FPassionate about showcasing these rare
OL,14,Fbreeds, the centre near Millom offers
OL,15,Funique riding experiences for people
OL,16,Fof all abilities and has an active
OL,17,Fbreeding programme.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
