PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1771949050
OL,3,C'We're not giving up': The horse
OL,4,Criding centre saving endangered breeds
OL,6,FBut protecting the gentle giants comes
OL,7,Fat a giant cost. Owner Annie Rose says
OL,8,Fskyrocketing prices for everyday items
OL,9,Flike hay, combined with an increase in
OL,10,FNational Insurance bills has pushed
OL,11,Fthe centre to a breaking point.
OL,13,F"Like everybody in business, overheads
OL,14,Fhave gone up but in the last year
OL,15,Fwe've had some real knock-backs,"
OL,16,FAnnie said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
