PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1771949050
OL,3,C'We're not giving up': The horse
OL,4,Criding centre saving endangered breeds
OL,6,F"The hike in national insurance costs
OL,7,Fhas pretty much destroyed us.
OL,8,FEverything that you buy in has gone up
OL,9,Fin the last few years. 10 years ago I
OL,10,Fcould buy a bale of hay for #24 - this
OL,11,Fyear it was nearly #60.
OL,13,F"My biggest cost is staff, but without
OL,14,Fthe staff this is nothing. I rely on
OL,15,Fthe to provide the quality that we do,
OL,16,Fthe service that we do."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
