PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1771949050
OL,3,C'We're not giving up': The horse
OL,4,Criding centre saving endangered breeds
OL,6,FAnnie has three Suffolk Punch mares,
OL,7,FBritain's oldest breed of heavy horse
OL,8,Fand classified as critically
OL,9,Fendangered by the Rare Breeds Survival
OL,10,FTrust.
OL,12,F"To be able to help them in that way
OL,13,Fis amazing," she said. "This year
OL,14,Fwe've got three Suffolk foals due and
OL,15,Fone Clydesdale - because I still love
OL,16,Fthe Scottish breed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
