PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1771949050
OL,3,C'We're not giving up': The horse
OL,4,Criding centre saving endangered breeds
OL,6,F"At one point, money made from the
OL,7,Friding side of the business would
OL,8,Fcover the extra costs but in the last
OL,9,Fyear it has become increasingly
OL,10,Fdifficult to make that work."
OL,12,FAnnie says she has been forced to sell
OL,13,Ffour of her horses, including a young
OL,14,FSuffolk Punch, and set up an online
OL,15,Ffundraising page to help cover the
OL,16,Fcentre's breeding programme.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
