FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1771949050
OL,3,C'We're not giving up': The horse
OL,4,Criding centre saving endangered breeds
OL,6,FAnnie says she is not prepared to give
OL,7,Fup on her passion and is now exploring
OL,8,Fdifferent income streams to keep her
OL,9,Fbusiness going, including a new
OL,10,Fpodcast focusing on the rare breeds.
OL,12,F"I've had to take a step back from the
OL,13,Fyard, which is really hard for me to
OL,14,Fdo," Annie said. "The business is my
OL,15,Flife and we are not giving up."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
