PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1771949050
OL,3,C'We're not giving up': The horse
OL,4,Criding centre saving endangered breeds
OL,6,FShe added: "We don't just do riding;
OL,7,Fwe work with children with special
OL,8,Feducational needs and bucket list with
OL,9,Fpeople who are terminally ill. We have
OL,10,Fto keep going because it's so special
OL,11,Fwhat we do here."
OL,13,FCumbrian Heavy Horses is not the only
OL,14,Friding centre feeling the pinch.
OL,15,FAccording to the The British Horse
OL,16,FSociety, 250 riding schools have
OL,17,Fclosed across the UK since 2018.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
