PN,39909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1771949050
OL,3,C'We're not giving up': The horse
OL,4,Criding centre saving endangered breeds
OL,6,FAnnie said: "That is a sad reflection
OL,7,Fof a equine industry as a whole
OL,8,Fbecause horses are phenomenally good
OL,9,Ffor people and I think it's a terrible
OL,10,Fshame that the overheads are so high
OL,11,Fthat people are having to close.
OL,13,F"Most (riding centre owners) don't
OL,14,Ftake an income, they just graft and
OL,15,Fwork seven days a week - I know this.
OL,16,FIt is a terrible shame that we're
OL,17,Flosing so many of them. I feel we are
OL,18,Fso under supported."
OL,26,@uD@GpmuD@\pn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
