PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1771949050
OL,3,C'We're not giving up': The horse
OL,4,Criding centre saving endangered breeds
OL,6,FSimone O'Connor, who works with
OL,7,FCumbrian Heavy Horses as an
OL,8,Finstructor, believes continuing to
OL,9,Fraise awareness of heavy horse breeds
OL,10,Fis crucial to their survival.
OL,12,F"It's an absolute privilege, it's hard
OL,13,Fwork and hard labour but what you put
OL,14,Fin you get back in spades," she said.
OL,16,FWant more on the issues effecting the
OL,17,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,18,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,19,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
